 '연세대학교_수시_082', '연세대학교_수시_071', '연세대학교_수시_015', '연세대학교_수시_138', '연세대학교_수시_179']\n","\n","\n","============================================================\n","🔍 쿼리: 고려대학교 경영학과 정시 모집인원은?\n","   자동 필터: {'university': '고려대학교', 'admission_type': '정시', 'dept_keyword': '경영학과'}\n","   ⚠️  결과 부족(1개) → 필터 완화 재검색: {'university': '고려대학교', 'admission_type': '정시'}\n","🤖 AI 답변 생성 중... (참고 문서 7개)\n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["Setting `pad_token_id` to `eos_token_id`:128001 for open-end generation.\n","Both `max_new_tokens` (=256) and `max_length`(=20) seem to have been set. `max_new_tokens` will take precedence. Please refer to the documentation for more information. (https://huggingface.co/docs/transformers/main/en/main_classes/text_generation)\n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\n","==================================================\n","✨ AI 최종 응답:\n","고려대학교 정시 경영학과 모집인원은 [문서 1]에 따르면 총 12명입니다.\n","==================================================\n","\n","참고 Doc IDs: ['고려대학교_정시_270', '고려대학교_정시_297', '고려대학교_정시_261', '고려대학교_정시_264', '고려대학교_정시_348', '고려대학교_정시_400', '고려대학교_정시_263']\n","\n","\n","============================================================\n","🔍 쿼리: 연세대 논술전형 수능 최저학력기준은?\n","   정규화: 연세대학교 논술전형 수능 최저학력기준은?\n","   자동 필터: {'university': '연세대학교'}\n","🤖 AI 답변 생성 중... (참고 문서 7개)\n","\n","==================================================\n","✨ AI 최종 응답:\n","[답변]: 연세대학교의 논술전형 수능 최저학력기준은 없습니다. 다만, 특기자전형, 기타 전형, 정시 전형의 경우에는 최저학력기준이 있습니다. 특기자전형의 경우에는 최저학력기준이 ①~④ 중 하나를 충족해야 하며, 기타 전형의 경우에는 최저학력기준이 ① 국내 고등학교 졸업(예정)자는 다음 두 가지 기준 중 하나를 충족해야 합니다. 정시 전형의 경우에는 최저학력기준이 없습니다. 또한, 수능시험 성적 총점 순으로 합격자를 선발하거나, 수능시험 성적과 2단계 면접평가 결과를 합산하여 총점 순으로 합격자를 선발합니다. 지원자 중 자격 요건을 갖추지 않은 자나 필수 서류를 기한 내 제출하지 않은 자는 입학전형 대상에서 제외합니다.\n","==================================================\n","\n","참고 Doc IDs: ['연세대학교_수시_003', '연세대학교_수시_104', '연세대학교_수시_088', '연세대학교_수시_077', '연세대학교_수시_168', '연세대학교_정시_2038', '연세대학교_수시_004']\n","\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["\"\"\"\n","04_evaluate_colab_v3.py  (속도 최적화 버전)\n","============================================\n","30분 → 1~2분으로 단축\n","\n","[핵심 최적화 2가지]\n","\n","1. 배치 임베딩 (가장 큰 병목 제거)\n","   - 이전: 쿼리 1개씩 model.encode() → 검색 1회당 0.5~1초\n","   - 이후: 전체 쿼리를 한 번에 배치 임베딩 → 검색 수백 회 분량을 수초 안에 처리\n","\n","2. 타입별 재평가 제거\n","   - 이전: 전체 평가 1회 + 타입별 재평가 5회 = 6배 검색\n","   - 이후: 전체 평가 1회 결과에서 타입별로 슬라이싱 (추가 검색 없음)\n","\n","사전 조건:\n","  - searcher = AdmissionSearcher()  (이전 셀에서 선언)\n","  - qa_pipe, generate_ai_qa         (QA 평가 시에만 필요)\n","\"\"\"\n","\n","import re, math, random, time, json\n","import numpy as np\n","from collections import defaultdict\n","from typing import Optional\n","\n","\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# 1. 평가셋 생성 (다중 정답 지원 - v2와 동일)\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","SUMMARY_PATTERN = re.compile(\n","    r'(.+?)\\s+(수시|정시)\\s+'\n","    r'([가-힣·()\\w]+(?:학과|학부|전공|의예과|치의예과|약학과|간호학과))\\s+'\n","    r'모집인원\\s+총\\s+(\\d+)명'\n",")\n","\n","SECTION_QUERY_TMPL = {\n","    \"수능최저\": \"{univ} {adm_type} {track}전형 수능 최저학력기준은?\",\n","    \"지원자격\": \"{univ} {adm_type} {track}전형 지원자격 조건은?\",\n","    \"제출서류\": \"{univ} {adm_type} {track}전형 제출서류 목록은?\",\n","    \"평가방법\": \"{univ} {adm_type} {track}전형 평가방법은?\",\n","}\n","\n","\n","def build_eval_dataset(data_path: str, seed: int = 42) -> list[dict]:\n","    with open(data_path, encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n","        data = json.load(f)\n","\n","    dept_to_docs   = defaultdict(list)\n","    dept_to_answer = {}\n","    for doc in data:\n","        ec = doc[\"enriched_content\"]\n","        if \"[전형별 모집인원 요약]\" not in ec:\n","            continue\n","        summary = ec[ec.find(\"[전형별 모집인원 요약]\"):]\n","        for m in SUMMARY_PATTERN.finditer(summary):\n","            univ, adm_type, dept, total = (\n","                m.group(1).strip(), m.group(2), m.group(3), m.group(4)\n","            )\n","            key = (univ, adm_type, dept)\n","            if doc[\"doc_id\"] not in dept_to_docs[key]:\n","                dept_to_docs[key].append(doc[\"doc_id\"])\n","            dept_to_answer[key] = total\n","\n","    evals = []\n","    for key, doc_ids in dept_to_docs.items():\n","        univ, adm_type, dept = key\n","        evals.append({\n","            \"query\":            f\"{univ} {dept} {adm_type} 모집인원 수는?\",\n","            \"query_type\":       \"모집인원\",\n","            \"relevant_doc_ids\": doc_ids,\n","            \"expected_answer\":  dept_to_answer[key],\n","            \"university\":       univ,\n","            \"admission_type\":   adm_type,\n","            \"dept\":             dept,\n","        })\n","\n","    section_to_docs = defaultdict(list)\n","    for doc in data:\n","        section = doc[\"section\"]\n","        if section not in SECTION_QUERY_TMPL:\n","            continue\n","        key = (doc[\"university\"], doc[\"admission_type\"], doc[\"track\"], section)\n","        if doc[\"doc_id\"] not in section_to_docs[key]:\n","            section_to_docs[key].append(doc[\"doc_id\"])\n","\n","    for key, doc_ids in section_to_docs.items():\n","        univ, adm_type, track, section = key\n","        track_str = track if track not in (\"기타\", \"공통\") else \"\"\n","        query = SECTION_QUERY_TMPL[section].format(\n","            univ=univ, adm_type=adm_type, track=track_str\n","        ).replace(\"  \", \" \").strip()\n","        evals.append({\n","            \"query\":            query,\n","            \"query_type\":       section,\n","            \"relevant_doc_ids\": doc_ids,\n","            \"expected_answer\":  None,\n","            \"university\":       univ,\n","            \"admission_type\":   adm_type,\n","            \"dept\":             None,\n","        })\n","\n","    random.seed(seed)\n","    random.shuffle(evals)\n","\n","    by_type = defaultdict(int)\n","    for e in evals:\n","        by_type[e[\"query_type\"]] += 1\n","    print(f\"  총 {len(evals)}개 케이스 생성\")\n","    for t, c in sorted(by_type.items()):\n","        print(f\"    - {t}: {c}개\")\n","    return evals\n","\n","\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# 2. 검색 지표\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","def hits_at_k(ranked, relevant, k):\n","    return float(any(d in relevant for d in ranked[:k]))\n","\n","def reciprocal_rank(ranked, relevant):\n","    for i, d in enumerate(ranked, 1):\n","        if d in relevant:\n","            return 1.0 / i\n","    return 0.0\n","\n","def ndcg_at_k(ranked, relevant, k):\n","    dcg  = sum(1.0 / math.log2(i + 2) for i, d in enumerate(ranked[:k]) if d in relevant)\n","    idcg = sum(1.0 / math.log2(i + 2) for i in range(min(len(relevant), k)))\n","    return dcg / idcg if idcg > 0 else 0.0\n","\n","\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# 3. 답변 품질 지표\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","NUM_PATTERN       = re.compile(r'\\d+')\n","NO_ANSWER_PHRASES = [\"정보 없음\", \"해당 정보가 문서에 없\", \"없습니다\", \"찾을 수 없\"]\n","\n","def answer_accuracy(response, expected):\n","    if expected is None:\n","        return None\n","    return 1.0 if expected in NUM_PATTERN.findall(response) else 0.0\n","\n","def is_no_answer(response):\n","    return any(p in response for p in NO_ANSWER_PHRASES)\n","\n","\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# 4. 핵심: 배치 검색 (속도 최적화)\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","def batch_search(searcher, cases: list[dict], top_k: int = 10, use_filters: bool = True) -> list[list[dict]]:\n","    \"\"\"\n","    전체 쿼리를 배치로 임베딩 후 FAISS 검색\n","    → 개별 encode() 반복 호출 제거로 수십 배 빠름\n","\n","    반환: cases와 같은 순서의 검색결과 리스트\n","    \"\"\"\n","    import faiss, numpy as np\n","\n","    queries = [c[\"query\"] for c in cases]\n","\n","    # 배치 임베딩 (핵심 최적화: 1번만 encode)\n","    print(f\"  ⚡ 배치 임베딩 생성 중... ({len(queries)}개 쿼리)\")\n","    t0 = time.time()\n","    query_vecs = searcher.model.encode(\n","        queries,\n","        batch_size=128,\n","        normalize_embeddings=True,\n","        convert_to_numpy=True,\n","        show_progress_bar=False,\n","    ).astype(np.float32)\n","    print(f\"     임베딩 완료 ({time.time()-t0:.1f}s)\")\n","\n","    # FAISS 배치 검색 (1번에 전체 쿼리 처리)\n","    fetch_k = min(top_k * 50, searcher.index.ntotal)\n","    t0 = time.time()\n","    all_scores, all_indices = searcher.index.search(query_vecs, fetch_k)\n","    print(f\"     FAISS 검색 완료 ({time.time()-t0:.2f}s)\")\n","\n","    # 각 쿼리별 필터 적용\n","    all_results = []\n","    for i, case in enumerate(cases):\n","        scores  = all_scores[i]\n","        indices = all_indices[i]\n","\n","        # 필터 구성\n","        univ_filter   = case.get(\"university\") if use_filters else None\n","        adm_filter    = case.get(\"admission_type\") if use_filters else None\n","\n","        results = []\n","        for score, idx in zip(scores, indices):\n","            if idx == -1:\n","                continue\n","            doc = searcher.meta[idx]\n","            if univ_filter and doc[\"university\"] != univ_filter:\n","                continue\n","            if adm_filter and doc[\"admission_type\"] != adm_filter:\n","                continue\n","            results.append({\"doc_id\": doc[\"doc_id\"], \"score\": float(score)})\n","            if len(results) >= top_k:\n","                break\n","        all_results.append(results)\n","\n","    return all_results\n","\n","\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","# 5. 메인 평가기\n","# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n","\n","class RAGEvaluator:\n","\n","    def __init__(self, searcher, data_path: str = \"admission_data_v2.json\"):\n","        self.searcher  = searcher\n","        self.data_path = data_path\n","        print(\"📋 평가셋 생성 중...\")\n","        self.eval_data = build_eval_dataset(data_path)\n","        print()\n","\n","    # ── 검색 평가 (배치 처리) ──────────────────────────────\n","    def _eval_retrieval(\n","        self, cases: list, top_k: int = 10, use_filters: bool = True\n","    ) -> dict:\n","        ks = [1, 3, 5, 10]\n","\n","        # ★ 배치 검색 (핵심: 1번 호출로 전체 처리)\n","        all_results = batch_search(self.searcher, cases, top_k=top_k, use_filters=use_filters)\n","\n","        hits  = {k: [] for k in ks}\n","        ndcgs = {k: [] for k in ks}\n","        rrs   = []\n","        per_case = []\n","\n","        for case, results in zip(cases, all_results):\n","            rel_ids = set(case[\"relevant_doc_ids\"])\n","            ranked  = [r[\"doc_id\"] for r in results]\n","            rr      = reciprocal_rank(ranked, rel_ids)\n","            rrs.append(rr)\n","\n","            row = {\n","                \"query\":        case[\"query\"],\n","                \"query_type\":   case[\"query_type\"],\n","                \"relevant_ids\": list(rel_ids),\n","                \"n_relevant\":   len(rel_ids),\n","                \"ranked_ids\":   ranked[:5],\n","                \"rr\":           round(rr, 4),\n","            }\n","            for k in ks:\n","                h = hits_at_k(ranked, rel_ids, k)\n","                n = ndcg_at_k(ranked, rel_ids, k)\n","                hits[k].append(h)\n","                ndcgs[k].append(n)\n","                row[f\"hits@{k}\"] = h\n","                row[f\"ndcg@{k}\"] = round(n, 4)\n","            per_case.append(row)\n","\n","        n = len(cases)\n","        return {\n","            \"n_cases\":  n,\n","            \"MRR\":      round(sum(rrs) / n, 4),\n","            **{f\"Hits@{k}\": round(sum(hits[k]) / n, 4) for k in ks},\n","            **{f\"nDCG@{k}\": round(sum(ndcgs[k]) / n, 4) for k in ks},\n","            \"per_case\": per_case,\n","        }\n","\n","    # ── QA 평가 ────────────────────────────────────────────\n","    def _eval_qa(self, cases, qa_pipe, generate_fn, top_k=7) -> dict:\n","        acc_scores = []\n","        no_ans_cnt = 0\n","        per_case   = []\n","        qa_cases   = [c for c in cases if c[\"expected_answer\"] is not None]\n","\n","        for i, case in enumerate(qa_cases):\n","            print(f\"   QA {i+1}/{len(qa_cases)}...\", end=\"\\r\")\n","            try:\n","                response = generate_fn(\n","                    case[\"query\"], self.searcher, qa_pipe,\n","                    top_k=top_k, verbose=False\n","                )\n","            except Exception as e:\n","                response = f\"[ERROR] {e}\"\n","\n","            acc  = answer_accuracy(response, case[\"expected_answer\"])\n","            noan = is_no_answer(response)\n","            if noan:\n","                no_ans_cnt += 1\n","            acc_scores.append(acc if acc is not None else 0.0)\n","            per_case.append({\n","                \"query\":        case[\"query\"],\n","                \"expected\":     case[\"expected_answer\"],\n","                \"response\":     response[:200],\n","                \"accuracy\":     acc,\n","                \"is_no_answer\": noan,\n","            })\n","\n","        print()\n","        n = len(qa_cases)\n","        return {\n","            \"n_cases\":        n,\n","            \"AnswerAccuracy\": round(sum(acc_scores) / n, 4) if n else 0,\n","            \"NoAnswerRate\":   round(no_ans_cnt / n, 4) if n else 0,\n","            \"per_case\":       per_case,\n","        }\n","\n","    # ── 통합 실행 ──────────────────────────────────────────\n","    def run(\n","        self,\n","        sample_n:    int  = 200,\n","        qa_pipe            = None,\n","        generate_fn        = None,\n","        run_qa:      bool = False,\n","        use_filters: bool = True,\n","        top_k_ret:   int  = 10,\n","        top_k_qa:    int  = 7,\n","        seed:        int  = 42,\n","        query_types: Optional[list] = None,\n","    ) -> dict:\n","\n","        random.seed(seed)\n","        cases = self.eval_data.copy()\n","        if query_types:\n","            cases = [c for c in cases if c[\"query_type\"] in query_types]\n","        if sample_n and sample_n < len(cases):\n","            cases = random.sample(cases, sample_n)\n","\n","        print(f\"🚀 평가 시작: {len(cases)}개 케이스 | 필터={'ON' if use_filters else 'OFF'}\")\n","        print()\n","\n","        # ── 검색 평가 (배치 1회로 처리) ───────────────────\n","        print(\"📡 [1/2] 검색 품질 평가 중...\")\n","        t0  = time.time()\n","        ret = self._eval_retrieval(cases, top_k=top_k_ret, use_filters=use_filters)\n","        elapsed = time.time() - t0\n","        print(f\"   완료 ({elapsed:.1f}s)\\n\")\n","\n","        # ★ 타입별 분석: 추가 검색 없이 per_case에서 슬라이싱\n","        type_results = {}\n","        by_type = defaultdict(list)\n","        for row in ret[\"per_case\"]:\n","            by_type[row[\"query_type\"]].append(row)\n","\n","        for qt, rows in by_type.items():\n","            n = len(rows)\n","            ks = [1, 3, 5, 10]\n","            type_results[qt] = {\n","                \"n_cases\": n,\n","                \"MRR\":     round(sum(r[\"rr\"] for r in rows) / n, 4),\n","                **{f\"Hits@{k}\": round(sum(r[f\"hits@{k}\"] for r in rows) / n, 4) for k in ks},\n","                **{f\"nDCG@{k}\": round(sum(r[f\"ndcg@{k}\"] for r in rows) / n, 4) for k in ks},\n","            }\n","\n","        # ── QA 평가 ───────────────────────────────────────\n","        qa_result = None\n","        if run_qa and qa_pipe and generate_fn:\n","            print(\"🤖 [2/2] QA 답변 품질 평가 중...\")\n","            qa_cases = [c for c in cases if c[\"query_type\"] == \"모집인원\"]\n","            if qa_cases:\n","                t0 = time.time()\n","                qa_result = self._eval_qa(qa_cases, qa_pipe, generate_fn, top_k=top_k_qa)\n","                print(f\"   완료 ({time.time()-t0:.1f}s)\\n\")\n","        else:\n","            print(\"ℹ️  [2/2] QA 평가 스킵 (run_qa=False)\\n\")\n","\n","        report = {\n","            \"config\": {\n","                \"sample_n\": len(cases), \"use_filters\": use_filters,\n","                \"top_k_ret\": top_k_ret, \"top_k_qa\": top_k_qa,\n","            },\n","            \"retrieval\":         ret,\n","            \"retrieval_by_type\": type_results,\n","            \"qa\":                qa_result,\n","        }\n","        self.print_report(report)\n","        return report\n","\n","    # ── 필터 ON/OFF 비교 (배치 처리) ──────────────────────\n","    def compare_filter(self, sample_n: int = 100, seed: int = 42):\n","        random.seed(seed)\n","        cases = random.sample(self.eval_data, min(sample_n, len(self.eval_data)))\n","        print(\"🔬 필터 ON vs OFF 비교\\n\")\n","\n","        print(\"  [필터 ON]\")\n","        r_on  = self._eval_retrieval(cases, use_filters=True)\n","        print(\"  [필터 OFF]\")\n","        r_off = self._eval_retrieval(cases, use_filters=False)\n","\n","        print(f\"\\n{'지표':<12} {'필터 ON':>10} {'필터 OFF':>10} {'차이':>8}\")\n","        print(\"-\" * 44)\n","        for m in [\"MRR\", \"Hits@1\", \"Hits@3\", \"Hits@5\", \"Hits@10\", \"nDCG@5\", \"nDCG@10\"]:\n","            on, off = r_on[m], r_off[m]\n","            delta = on - off\n","            print(f\"{m:<12} {on:>10.4f} {off:>10.4f} {'+' if delta>=0 else ''}{delta:>7.4f}\")\n","        print()\n","\n","    # ── 결과 출력 ──────────────────────────────────────────\n","    @staticmethod\n","    def print_report(report: dict):\n","        r   = report[\"retrieval\"]\n","        cfg = report[\"config\"]\n","\n","        print(\"=\" * 62)\n","        print(\"📊 RAG 평가 리포트\")\n","        print(\"=\" * 62)\n","        print(f\"  평가 케이스 수 : {cfg['sample_n']}개\")\n","        print(f\"  필터 사용      : {'ON' if cfg['use_filters'] else 'OFF'}\")\n","        print()\n","\n","        print(\"┌─ 검색 품질 ──────────────────────────────────────┐\")\n","        print(f\"│  MRR       : {r['MRR']:.4f}   (평균 역순위, 높을수록 상위 노출)\")\n","        print(f\"│  Hits@1    : {r['Hits@1']:.4f}  ({r['Hits@1']*100:.1f}%)  1위가 정답인 비율\")\n","        print(f\"│  Hits@3    : {r['Hits@3']:.4f}  ({r['Hits@3']*100:.1f}%)  3위 안에 정답\")\n","        print(f\"│  Hits@5    : {r['Hits@5']:.4f}  ({r['Hits@5']*100:.1f}%)  5위 안에 정답\")\n","        print(f\"│  Hits@10   : {r['Hits@10']:.4f}  ({r['Hits@10']*100:.1f}%)  10위 안에 정답\")\n","        print(f\"│  nDCG@5    : {r['nDCG@5']:.4f}   (순위 감쇠 반영 품질)\")\n","        print(f\"│  nDCG@10   : {r['nDCG@10']:.4f}   (순위 감쇠 반영 품질)\")\n","        print(\"└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\")\n","\n","        h5, mrr = r[\"Hits@5\"], r[\"MRR\"]\n","        grade = (\n","            \"🟢 양호 (실사용 가능)\" if h5 >= 0.75 and mrr >= 0.6 else\n","            \"🟡 보통 (개선 권장)\"   if h5 >= 0.5  and mrr >= 0.4 else\n","            \"🔴 미흡 (개선 필요)\"\n","        )\n","        print(f\"  → 종합 판정: {grade}\")\n","        print()\n","\n","        if report.get(\"retrieval_by_type\"):\n","            print(\"┌─ 유형별 Hits@5 / MRR ──────────────────────────────┐\")\n","            for qt, res in sorted(report[\"retrieval_by_type\"].items()):\n","                h5t  = res.get(\"Hits@5\", 0)\n","                flag = \"⚠️ \" if h5t < 0.3 else \"   \"\n","                print(f\"│ {flag}[{qt:6s}]  Hits@5={h5t:.3f}  MRR={res.get('MRR',0):.3f}  (n={res['n_cases']})\")\n","            print(\"└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\")\n","            print()\n","\n","        if report.get(\"qa\"):\n","            qa  = report[\"qa\"]\n","            acc = qa[\"AnswerAccuracy\"]\n","            grade_qa = \"🟢 양호\" if acc >= 0.7 else \"🟡 보통\" if acc >= 0.5 else \"🔴 미흡\"\n","            print(\"┌─ QA 답변 품질 ────────────────────────────────────┐\")\n","            print(f\"│  AnswerAccuracy : {acc:.4f}  ({acc*100:.1f}%)  → {grade_qa}\")\n","            print(f\"│  NoAnswerRate   : {qa['NoAnswerRate']:.4f}  ({qa['NoAnswerRate']*100:.1f}%)  (낮을수록 좋음)\")\n","            print(f\"│  평가 케이스    : {qa['n_cases']}개\")\n","            print(\"└──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\")\n","            print()\n","\n","        failed = [c for c in r[\"per_case\"] if c.get(\"hits@5\", 1) == 0]\n","        if failed:\n","            print(f\"⚠️  Hits@5=0 케이스: {len(failed)}개 / {r['n_cases']}개 (샘플 5개)\")\n","            for c in failed[:5]:\n","                print(f\"   [{c['query_type']}] {c['query'][:55]}\")\n","                print(f\"         정답={c['relevant_ids'][:2]}  |  검색상위={c['ranked_ids'][:3]}\")\n","            print()\n","\n","    # ── 저장 ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n","    @staticmethod\n","    def save_report(report: dict, path: str = \"eval_report.json\"):\n","        slim = {\n","            \"config\":            report[\"config\"],\n","            \"retrieval_summary\": {k: v for k, v in report[\"retrieval\"].items() if k != \"per_case\"},\n","            \"retrieval_by_type\": report.get(\"retrieval_by_type\", {}),\n","            \"qa_summary\": (\n","                {k: v for k, v in report[\"qa\"].items() if k != \"per_case\"}\n","                if report.get(\"qa\") else None\n","            ),\n","        }\n","        with open(path, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n","            json.dump(slim, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n","        print(f\"✅ 저장 완료: {path}\")\n","\n","    # ── 실패 케이스 분석 ───────────────────────────────────\n","    def analyze_failures(self, report: dict, top_n: int = 10):\n","        per_case = report[\"retrieval\"][\"per_case\"]\n","        failed   = [c for c in per_case if c.get(\"hits@10\", 1) == 0]\n","        print(f\"❌ Hits@10=0 케이스: {len(failed)}개\\n\")\n","        by_type = defaultdict(list)\n","        for c in failed:\n","            by_type[c[\"query_type\"]].append(c)\n","        for qt, cases in sorted(by_type.items()):\n","            print(f\"  [{qt}] {len(cases)}개\")\n","            for c in cases[:top_n]:\n","                print(f\"    Q  : {c['query']}\")\n","                print(f\"    정답: {c['relevant_ids'][:2]}\")\n","                print(f\"    검색: {c['ranked_i